=71305bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9cea33a7f1b7f11ba64107d64d9c7fc0ba818139","tid":1486260,"uid":233648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:42:52.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e55ef2c05f499ef55b80e84f945280e26046f5","tid":1486260,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:47:49.000Z","msg":"必須推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4336d2c6947d288e0e1be20863595d8eeb9613","tid":1486260,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:51:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分和勇</span></span>"},{"pid":"7360465fab213d77d33c9d1f88bcae8b9cfcf468","tid":1486260,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:52:29.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;衝就係鬼&rdquo;呢句說話真係覆水難收，之後嘅遊行個個都加句和理非先有人去，而和理非就叫衝就係鬼，咁就仆街啦。再俾我聽到衝就係鬼，我會拖實個左膠隻手唔放，一齊食催淚彈。"},{"pid":"a87a277fae4d85ccc76512bcbdf3c49c4f109997","tid":1486260,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b131daee3ec3edf75bc1421dbed92d99888791c9","tid":1486260,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:54:14.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"0dc84999fc37a7f439ce7ee0bc7efbfd6483decc","tid":1486260,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:57:52.000Z","msg":"大撚把on9仲係分緊兩種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋定性衝衝子真係會on9無腦咁衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a4be03acaacc9062fffa6ed2949063b1f25ea2","tid":1486260,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dis