ike":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:24:15.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly<br />\n和理非同勇武係一種手段，而非身分<br />\nBe water, my friend<br />\nEmpty your mind, be formless, shapeless, like water. Put water into a cup. Becomes the cup. Put water into a teapot. Becomes the teapot. <br />\n<br />\nbe Water係唔好俾自己俾自己嘅身份去限制自己嘅思想同行為<br />\n喺唔同嘅情況底下，你可以選擇唔同嘅行為同手段<br />\n係樽嘅時候你會變成樽，係杯嘅時候你會變成係杯<br />\n只要目標無變<br />\n大家若果識得靈活使用唔同手段，咁就能夠以有限資源做更多嘅事<br />\n<br />\n從來大家只係得一個身份一個標籤就係香港人<br />\n無論係男係女老年中年淨係青年<br />\n無論係咩職業，無論係向前衝抑或是做後援<br />\n大家只有一個身份：真 &middot; 香港人"},{"pid":"959e943139cd4848d64bbd2649733deab40dca41","tid":1486260,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:26:25.000Z","msg":"【團結就是力量】前線、後勤 取替 勇武、和理非<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2844bfa8ad643462850d05034d1046edb7526e51","tid":1486260,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f0232db18035ddea0ae7f6e5c9c2273b9cbc59","tid":1486260,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:29:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"80af867568707f5c921749a34b746c4185da857a","tid":1486260,"uid":119188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:31:20.000Z","msg":"係手足啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c0bb915d16d36ff673b81a5bd63e7311f34f6e","tid":1486260,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229a054486149e98564527da14e457f1041e9c9c","tid":1486260,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT